lunamark -Xbracketed_spans
<<<
[text]{.myclass}.

[text]{lang=fr}.

[text]{#hash}.

[text]{}.

[text]{ #hash .my-class lang="fr" }.

[text]{.underline}
>>>
<p><span class="myclass">text</span>.</p>
<p><span lang="fr">text</span>.</p>
<p><span id="hash">text</span>.</p>
<p><span>text</span>.</p>
<p><span id="hash" class="my-class" lang="fr">text</span>.</p>
<p><u class="underline">text</u></u></p>
